cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is about a method for incorporating multiple languages into vision-language models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also deals with visual data, which suggests the category cs.CV (Computer Vision). The method involves learning a shared embedding, which is a common technique in machine learning, indicating the category cs.LG (Learning). The paper also involves deep learning, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence, suggesting the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with multimodal data, which suggests the category cs.MM (Multimedia).
